                    data-isverify="False"
                    data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/1761056/new_review">
                    <span>我要写书评</span>
                </a>
            <h2>
                    蓝石头的书评 · · · · · ·

